! STEOM-CCSD STO-3G TightSCF
# H2O sto-3g, DEFAULT frozen core (= O1s = 1 orbital; avoids EWin syntax).
# COMPLETE active space (NActIP 4 = all active occ, NActEA 2 = all active vir).
# Decisive validation of the determinant-Fock-space STEOM ground truth.
# Candidates for lowest singlet (eV), frozen=1, complete active:
#   determinant STEOM (plain expm): 11.847
#   analytic build_g_canonical_full: 10.691
#   EOM-EE-CCSD                     : 11.714
# If ORCA ~= 11.85 -> determinant is the correct oracle ({e^S} unneeded).
# If ORCA ~= 10.69 -> analytic right / determinant needs {e^S}.
%mdci
  nroots 6
  DoSTEOM true
  DoCISNat false
  NActIP 4
  NActEA 2
end
* xyz 0 1
O    0.000     0.000     0.127
H    0.000     0.758    -0.509
H    0.000    -0.758    -0.509
